title: Asset Listing: Add $LON on ETH v1
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list $LON on ETH v1 with a collateral factor and collateral cap.

Proposal: https://forum.cream.finance/t/new-asset-proposal-lon-tokenlon/1815

Rationale: List $LON on ETH v1 market with collateral factor of 45% and collateral cap of $500k (204,082 LON). Tokenlon is a decentralized exchange and payment protocol.

For:  List $LON on ETH v1 market with Collateral Factor: 45% and Collateral Cap: $500k (204,082 LON).

Against:  Do nothing.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
